const ShareIcon = ({ active }) => {
    return(
        <button className="p-2 hover:bg-slate-500 hover:bg-opacity-10 [&:hover_path]:stroke-slate-300 transition duration-100 rounded-full ">
            <svg className={`${active && 'fill-slate-500 [&_path]:stroke-slate-500'} w-5 h-5`} fill="#ffffff" width="800px" height="800px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" id="retweet-round-2" data-name="Flat Line" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon flat-line">
            <g id="SVGRepo_bgCarrier" stroke-width="0"/>
            <g id="SVGRepo_tracerCarrier" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            <g id="SVGRepo_iconCarrier">
            <path className="transition-colors duration-100" id="primary" d="M16.89,18.46A6,6,0,0,1,6,15V10"/>
            <path id="primary-2" data-name="primary" d="M7.11,5.54A6,6,0,0,1,18,9v5"/>
            <polyline id="primary-3" data-name="primary" points="4 12 6 10 8 12" />
            <polyline id="primary-4" data-name="primary" points="20 12 18 14 16 12" />
            </g>
            </svg>
        </button>   
    )
}

export default ShareIcon;
